708
01:05:27,636 --> 01:05:32,057
I mean, this... this is the most important thing
that's ever happened to me.

709
01:05:32,141 --> 01:05:36,353
I mean, this is...
this is the most... important thing...

710
01:05:36,437 --> 01:05:40,566
...that I have ever done in my whole life,
in my whole stupid life!

711
01:05:40,649 --> 01:05:42,735
And you want me to just stop?!

712
01:05:44,320 --> 01:05:46,947
No! No, I won't stop!

713
01:05:47,031 --> 01:05:49,450
I won't stop! I won't stop!

714
01:05:51,619 --> 01:05:54,330
Eight years, I've known you.

715
01:05:54,413 --> 01:05:58,417
Not once have you talked to me like this.
Not once.

716
01:05:58,501 --> 01:06:02,379
And if you do it again, I swear to God...

717
01:06:03,422 --> 01:06:09,220
And you know what? When you talk about
how ordinary you are and your stupid life,...

718
01:06:09,303 --> 01:06:14,225
...you're saying "Our stupid life,"
which I don't think is particularly stupid.

719
01:06:14,308 --> 01:06:18,145
So how the fuck
am I supposed to feel about that?

720
01:07:12,992 --> 01:07:15,369
Are you gonna drink that?

721
01:07:27,715 --> 01:07:29,425
I'm sorry.

722
01:07:31,760 --> 01:07:34,096
OK, I'm not sorry.

723
01:07:40,978 --> 01:07:43,606
- Who's that from?
- My brother Steve.

724
01:07:43,689 --> 01:07:47,526
- My grandma's going back in the hospital.
- No, she...

725
01:07:48,569 --> 01:07:50,029
What?

726
01:07:52,448 --> 01:07:53,991
What?

727
01:07:55,367 --> 01:07:57,077
Nothing.

728
01:08:07,004 --> 01:08:09,256
What is it?

729
01:08:16,972 --> 01:08:18,516
Hello?

730
01:08:18,599 --> 01:08:22,812
Oh, Steve. I'm sorry, we've been so busy.
I was just about...

731
01:08:22,895 --> 01:08:24,980
What?

732
01:08:29,026 --> 01:08:31,570
She did?

733
01:08:32,446 --> 01:08:34,532
How am I doing, Dad?

734
01:08:34,615 --> 01:08:37,576
You're doing great, kid. You're doing great.

735
01:08:43,207 --> 01:08:45,709
I'm so sorry, baby.

736
01:08:48,462 --> 01:08:50,673
You knew.

737
01:08:50,756 --> 01:08:52,842
You knew, didn't you?

738
01:08:52,925 --> 01:08:55,469
When is the funeral?

739
01:08:55,553 --> 01:08:59,682
Sunday. We should leave as soon as we can.

740
01:08:59,765 --> 01:09:01,851
Oh.

741
01:09:01,934 --> 01:09:04,437
You... you want me to go with you?

742
01:09:06,063 --> 01:09:08,774
I just thought,
with your family and everything...

743
01:09:08,858 --> 01:09:12,820
Do I want you to go with me...
to my grandmother's funeral?

744
01:09:12,903 --> 01:09:16,031
She practically raised me!
Of course I want you to come.

745
01:09:16,115 --> 01:09:20,578
It's just, I'm kinda
in the middle of something here.

746
01:10:28,395 --> 01:10:32,024
$800 a month! Can't get any fucking water!

747
01:10:32,108 --> 01:10:34,193
Fuck!

748
