Damn!

750
01:12:42,613 --> 01:12:44,698
Piece of shit!

751
01:13:23,112 --> 01:13:26,240
Haa-ha-ha-ha!

752
01:13:26,907 --> 01:13:27,950
Yaaaaa!

753
01:13:39,003 --> 01:13:41,088
It's a rented house!

754
01:13:57,521 --> 01:13:59,356
- Hello?
- It's me.

755
01:13:59,440 --> 01:14:02,568
- Oh, hey. Hey, baby, how're ya doin'?
- I'm OK.

756
01:14:02,651 --> 01:14:06,781
- How's your family?
- Drunk, fighting with each other.

757
01:14:06,864 --> 01:14:11,368
Listen, Maggie, I'm so sorry. I mean, I...
I should be there with ya. I'm an asshole.

758
01:14:11,452 --> 01:14:14,205
Yeah, well, you have your good points.

759
01:14:14,288 --> 01:14:18,167
- How do you feel?
- Oh, fine. Fine. You know...

760
01:14:18,250 --> 01:14:22,129
Much... much... much better.
Everything's fine here. Really good.

761
01:14:22,213 --> 01:14:25,424
No, uh...

762
01:14:26,217 --> 01:14:30,596
- No more digging?
- No. Uh-uh. Back to normal.

763
01:14:30,679 --> 01:14:35,601
I'm sorry, too. I wish I hadn't stormed out.
I shouldn't have left you alone.

764
01:14:35,684 --> 01:14:37,853
