for personal trips.

768
01:14:48,197 --> 01:14:54,286
I'll pick you up. I'll leave right away.

769
01:14:50,282 --> 01:14:53,869
Oh, no, no, baby. Don't do that. That's crazy.

770
01:14:53,953 --> 01:14:55,871
I gotta go.

771
01:14:55,955 --> 01:14:58,958
- I'll just pull up front and honk. Bye.
- No, no, no! No!

772
01:15:38,539 --> 01:15:40,749
OK, bub, you ready to go?

773
01:15:40,833 --> 01:15:43,961
I'm scared to go home.
I wanna stay at Uncle Steve's house.

774
01:15:44,044 --> 01:15:48,632
- Why are you scared?
- Because of the feathers.

775
01:15:48,924 --> 01:15:51,218
What feathers?

776
01:15:51,302 --> 01:15:54,013
I don't know. I just saw feathers.

777
01:15:55,806 --> 01:15:58,309
It's OK. I'll watch him.

778
01:15:58,392 --> 01:16:00,811
OK. You be good.

779
01:16:00,895 --> 01:16:03,189
Mom! Wait!

780
01:16:04,648 --> 01:16:06,942
You forgot this.

781
01:18:26,665 --> 01:18:28,959
Hi!

782
01:18:30,002 --> 01:18:31,712
Hi.

783
01:18:31,796 --> 01:18:34,340
Come here a sec.

784
01:18:34,423 --> 01:18:38,636
- What?
- Come closer. I can't hear you.

785
01:18:40,638 --> 01:18:44,683
- Are you talking to me?
- I wanna show you something.

786
01:18:44,767 --> 01:18:46,852
You wanna show me something?

787
01:18:46,936 --> 01:18:50,064
Well, yeah. I don't see anybody else around.

788
01:18:51,107 --> 01:18:54,110
