791
01:19:07,039 --> 01:19:09,125
Hey! Happy St Patrick's Day!

792
01:19:09,208 --> 01:19:12,044
- What's the surprise?
- Don't you have it?

793
01:19:12,128 --> 01:19:15,089
- Oh, yeah. The surprise, huh?
- The surprise.

794
01:19:15,172 --> 01:19:17,716
- You need another drink.
- No, I got the spins.

795
01:19:17,800 --> 01:19:19,885
Drink, motherfucker, drink!

796
01:19:19,969 --> 01:19:24,056
- I don't think there is a surprise.
- Oh, yeah, there is. Yeah, there is.

797
01:19:24,140 --> 01:19:26,851
The surprise is we decided
we wanna be your friends.

798
01:19:26,934 --> 01:19:28,686
- You do?
- Yeah.

799
01:19:28,769 --> 01:19:33,357
- Why do you wanna be my friends now?
- Are you kidding? Look at yourself.

800
01:19:35,401 --> 01:19:37,987
Uh-uh, look.

801
01:19:38,070 --> 01:19:40,823
You can take your coat off, you know.

802
01:19:41,532 --> 01:19:44,285
- You want a drink?
- I'm not supposed to.

803
01:19:44,368 --> 01:19:48,456
Don't you do anything
you're not supposed to? Huh?

804
01:19:48,539 --> 01:19:50,833
I do.

805
01:19:52,751 --> 01:19:54,211
Yeah.

806
01:19:54,295 --> 01:19:56,797
Momma, you are hot!

807
01:19:56,881 --> 01:20:00,176
Come on, let's be friends, huh?

808
01:20:00,259 --> 01:20:02,553
Well,...

809
01:20:02,636 --> 01:20:05,389
...you can kiss me if you want to.

810
01:20:05,473 --> 01:20:07,975
Yeah... Yeah.

811
01:20:16,484 --> 01:20:19,987
- Not... not like that, OK?
- OK. OK. OK...

812
01:20:25,034 --> 01:20:27,328
Agh! Ouch!

813
01:20:29,663 --> 01:20:34,376
- I wanna go home.
- Not now, no, no. Come on...

814
01:20:34,460 --> 01:20:36,545
- I'll be your friend.
- I want to, but...

815
01:20:36,629 --> 01:20:40,466
Just be nice to me, huh? Be a good girl.
You are a good girl, aren't you?

816
01:20:40,549 --> 01:20:43,511
- I have to go home.
- How about a helmet wash?

817
01:20:43,594 --> 01:20:46,388
I have to go home. I have to go home!

818
01:20:56,148 --> 01:20:58,567
No! Stop!

819
