Shut up! Shut up!

820
01:21:03,239 --> 01:21:05,324
Shut... Argh! God!

821
01:21:05,407 --> 01:21:08,536
Shut up! Argh!

822
01:21:10,162 --> 01:21:12,998
Make her stop, man!
Make her stop screaming!

823
01:21:13,082 --> 01:21:14,500
Shut her up, man!

824
01:21:18,462 --> 01:21:21,132
