831
01:21:57,668 --> 01:22:00,921
- Look at her tongue, man.
- I am not here.

832
01:22:01,005 --> 01:22:03,466
I've never seen nobody dead before.

833
01:22:03,549 --> 01:22:06,177
- I can't be here.
- It's fucking gross.

834
01:22:06,260 --> 01:22:08,804
