I'm gonna head over.

840
01:23:03,734 --> 01:23:06,070
Frank... I'm sorry.

841
01:23:07,113 --> 01:23:12,743
I'm sorry because...
I think I know why Adam shot himself.

842
01:23:13,327 --> 01:23:16,747
And... I gotta call the police about it.

843
01:23:17,873 --> 01:23:20,543
And I don't want you to hear it from them.

844
01:23:20,626 --> 01:23:23,963
And I don't want Sheila
to read about it in the paper.

845
01:23:24,046 --> 01:23:28,426
I-I... I think you have a right to know
before anybody else.

846
01:23:28,509 --> 01:23:30,761
What are you talking about, Tom?

847
01:23:33,597 --> 01:23:36,100
Come with me.

848
01:23:36,183 --> 01:23:38,894
Wait here for a second.

849
01:23:46,193 --> 01:23:49,113
It better be important.

850
01:24:00,499 --> 01:24:03,127
Come on!
Come on, come on, come on, come on!

851
01:24:06,172 --> 01:24:08,424
How the hell did you find this?

852
01:24:09,008 --> 01:24:11,469
Does it matter?

853
01:24:12,511 --> 01:24:15,139
Well, you don't know if it was Kurt and Adam.

854
01:24:16,098 --> 01:24:18,017
Yeah, I do.

855
01:24:19,435 --> 01:24:21,979
But you don't have anything to...

856
01:24:23,022 --> 01:24:28,611
Tom, you're talking like a goddamn lunatic!
That's what people are gonna say.

857
01:24:28,694 --> 01:24:31,614
I-it's just a body. It doesn't prove anything.

858
01:24:32,406 --> 01:24:33,949
She's...

859
01:24:34,033 --> 01:24:37,244
She's got somebody's hair in her hand.

860
01:24:38,287 --> 01:24:41,415
They're gonna be able to tell whose it is.

861
01:24:45,169 --> 01:24:47,546
Hey, Frank.

862
01:24:50,132 --> 01:24:52,968
We... we gotta call the cops.

863
01:24:55,221 --> 01:24:58,599
What were we supposed to do?

864
01:24:59,100 --> 01:25:01,727
It was an accident.

865
01:25:03,771 --> 01:25:07,358
The kids come to us, she's already dead.

866
01:25:08,609 --> 01:25:13,239
The damage is done. There's nothing
anybody can do to bring her back.

867
01:25:14,698 --> 01:25:19,578
But these kids got...
everything ahead of them.

868
01:25:20,871 --> 01:25:23,749
So what were we supposed to do, Tom?

869
01:25:23,833 --> 01:25:28,170
Send our sons to jail for the rest of their lives
because of her?

870
01:25:29,213 --> 01:25:31,674
Who are you planning to shoot with that?

871
01:25:33,217 --> 01:25:37,221
- Get the hell outta here, Tom.
- Hey, Frank... come on upstairs.

872
01:25:37,304 --> 01:25:39,348
We... we could talk about this.

873
01:25:39,432 --> 01:25:42,810
I've been living with this for... six months.

874
01:25:46,105 --> 01:25:49,024
Six fucking months!

875
01:25:50,776 --> 01:25:56,157
Do you think anything you have to say is
gonna make one bit of difference to me?!

876
01:25:57,241 --> 01:26:00,411
- Get the hell outta here!
- I-I'm not leaving until...

877
01:26:00,494 --> 01:26:01,662
Get out!

878
01:26:02,788 --> 01:26:05,040
Get out!

879
01:26:16,010 --> 01:26:19,805
- Hi.
- Hi. Hi.

880
01:26:20,097 --> 01:26:24,894
- Well, it's really pouring, huh?
- Yeah, looks like it.

881
01:26:25,436 --> 01:26:28,689
You got a minute?

882
01:26:28,773 --> 01:26:31,358
No, I'm... I'm... kinda busy right now.

883
01:26:31,442 --> 01:26:33,444
It's important.

884
