What the hell you think
you're doing to my house?

892
01:27:08,771 --> 01:27:11,941
I heard all this pounding going on.
I thought I'd check it out.

893
01:27:12,024 --> 01:27:14,652
I didn't think you'd be wrecking the place!

894
01:27:15,194 --> 01:27:17,738
What's the matter with you?

895
01:27:17,822 --> 01:27:21,492
Oh, don't worry. I'm gonna...
I'm gonna take care of that.

896
01:27:21,575 --> 01:27:25,162
I-I was trying to fix your water main,
you know - it was leaking,...

897
01:27:25,246 --> 01:27:28,415
...and I couldn't get to it
from underneath the house.

898
01:27:29,750 --> 01:27:34,630
I-I mean... I-I couldn't
get under the house to get to it.

899
01:27:35,756 --> 01:27:38,342
Is that right?

900
01:27:39,427 --> 01:27:42,179
Damn. A lotta water damage?

901
01:27:42,930 --> 01:27:45,558
Some.

902
01:27:45,641 --> 01:27:47,935
Can I look around?

903
01:27:49,437 --> 01:27:53,399
Yeah. Yeah, sure. Sure. Help yourself.

904
01:27:55,067 --> 01:27:57,403
Maybe you'd better show me where it's at.

